scoringPlays.text: Jeremy McNichols 61 Yd pass from Cedrick Wilson (Tyler Rausa Kick)
Thomas Sperbeck 5 Yd pass from Brett Rypien (Tyler Rausa Kick)
Cedrick Wilson 36 Yd pass from Brett Rypien (Tyler Rausa Kick)
Andrew Rodriguez 30 Yd pass from Kent Myers (Brock Warren Kick)

videos.description: Boise State quarterback Brett Rypien throws it behind the line of scrimmage to Cedrick Wilson, who then fires a deep ball to Jeremy McNichols for the 61-yard touchdown to give the Broncos a 7-0 lead over Utah State.
videos.headline: Boise State uses trick play to open the scoring

videos.description: Brett Rypien pass complete to Thomas Sperbeck for 5 yds for a TD
videos.headline: B. Rypien pass,to T. Sperbeck for 5 yds for a TD

videos.description: Utah State's Anthony Williams hits Boise State's returner Akilian Butler before he can catch the ball on a punt return. Williams would be ejected for targeting.
videos.headline: Utah State player ejected for clothesline of Boise State's punt returner

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Utah State player ejected for clotheslining Boise State punt returner) 2016/10/01
